    "description": "Grow your career with New India Assurance Advisory Limited! We are hiring a Credit Analyst for our Ahmedabad team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout New India Assurance Advisory Limited:\nNew India Assurance Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Process payroll and manage employee reimbursements\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n• Proficiency in Financial Reporting\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in Bloomberg Terminal\n• Proficiency in Python for Finance\n• Proficiency in Power BI\n• Proficiency in GST\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Referral bonus program\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with New India Assurance Advisory Limited!",
